When using flex box, we can combine it with margin to create some reall cool  grids. 

// flex container
.detail{
    display: flex;
}



// flex items
.description{
    background-color: orangered;
    flex: 60%;
    margin-right: 4.5rem;
    margin-left: 4.5rem;
}

.user-reviews{
  background-color: greenyellow;
  flex: 40%;
  margin-right: 4.5rem;
  margin-left: 4.5rem;
}
